data.title: Harmony Embroidered Scallop by Peacock Alley
data.meta_description: The timeless scalloped sheet now has a twist. Introducing Harmony, our new white percale sheet with a graceful embroidered scalloped edge and coordinating hemstitch. Available in subtle colors designed to pair flawlessly with many of our bedding products. The result is clean, fresh and timeless.
